    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
此度、門為参候て海山の咄御国の咄も聞つくし、誠におもしろく奉<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>存候。然、私の心中などのこらず此の為に咄有<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>之候間、くは敷御聞取可<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>被<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>遣と存候。稽首。<lb />
<span rend="jisage_3" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 3em">正月廿二日<span rend="chitsuki_2" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 2em">龍馬</span></span>
<span rend="jisage_5" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 5em">坂本乙様　左右<span rend="chitsuki_2" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 2em">直柔</span></span>
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
